Package: stppSim
Type: Package
Title: Spacio-Temporal Point Pattern Simulation for Social Science Research
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Monsuru Adepeju [cre, aut]
Maintainer: MOnsuru Adepeju <monsuur2010@yahoo.com>
Description: Designed for simulating socio-related point pattern with 
  both spatial and temporal signatures within a confined
  geographical and time boundaries. Social phenomena, such as crime 
  and diseases fall into this category. The package is suitable 
  for testing and evaluation of models for social science research. 
Language: en-US
License: GPL-3
URL: https://github.com/MAnalytics/stppSim
BugReports: https://github.com/Manalytics/stppSim/issues/new/choose
Depends: R (>= 4.0.0)
Encoding: UTF-8
